history.content: @2323 is for non-transfer juniors. EECS junior transfers have seats reserved for them in EE16AB, however I am hearing from EECS transfers that they're not able to enroll. I've contacted SIS to find out what's going on and will keep you posted. I recommend waitlisting for this class in the meantime.

I am a junior transfer eecs but I got the following message when I try to enroll in EE16B.

Error:  You are unable to enroll in this class at this time. Available seats are reserved and you do not meet the reserve capacity requirements. If a wait list is available, you may still be placed on the waitlist for this class. To do this, select Add Another Class to return to step 1. Select the class link, select the wait list option and resubmit your request.
